---------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
     http://www-zeuthen.desy.de/~alekhin/OPENQCDRAD/ 

 FONLL general-mass variable-flavor-number scheme: (for HF_SCHEME = 'FONLL-A', 'FONLL-B', 'FONLL-C') from APFEL
